metadata.name: SOAR
metadata.description:
A self-portrait and a poem by me as an expression of gratitude for appreciating and supporting the art pouring from my heart/soul! üôè‚ù§Ô∏è‚òÄÔ∏è

Love,  
Ava üòªüíÉ


The doors are open  
The windows shining bright with light  
The darkness beckons  
There is no need to fight.  
Just venture forth  
Alone and unafraid  
The mystery reveals itself  
To those who know to wait.  
The yearning  
The body  
The senses  
Are calling  
Follow the feeling  
Elusive,  
Elated,  
Soaring.
